nodes.text: Star Wars Miniatures: Ultimate Missions: Rebel Storm

Star Wars Miniatures: Ultimate Missions: Rebel Storm was a book based on the figures from the Star Wars Miniatures Rebel Storm set that included thirty-three game scenarios, as well as extra maps and map tiles (Mos Eisley spaceport, and Cloud City). It was released on November 30, 2004 by Wizards of the Coast.
